Package com.ibm.as400.access

Class SQLNativeType

java.lang.Object
com.ibm.as400.access.SQLNativeType
public class SQLNativeType extends Object

Class containing constants for the native SQL type values. The number is included in the definition for ease of debugging the values when viewed in the data stream.
